N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 23 ยง 102.5 - Penalties/Enforcement Actions

State Regulations

All Licensees shall be subject to all applicable penalties, including late fees and interest, provided for by the FSL, the State Finance

Law or other applicable laws. Enforcement actions for nonpayment could include
suspension, revocation, expiration or termination of a person's license or such
other actions as the superintendent may deem appropriate. Notes
